When it's from Maddie, she cries.

00:25:18.750 --> 00:25:20.752 line:95%,end
I'm gonna take Mackenzie
to the hospital.

00:25:20.819 --> 00:25:23.255 line:95%,end
- What do you mean, the hospital?
- Her foot is killing her.

00:25:24.356 --> 00:25:25.590 line:95%,end
Hey.

00:25:25.657 --> 00:25:27.292 line:95%,end
Excuse me for just a moment.

00:25:27.492 --> 00:25:29.127 line:95%,end
- Hi.
- Don't touch me.

00:25:29.461 --> 00:25:31.963 line:95%,end
You looked like you were,
you know, about to hit the wings,

00:25:32.030 --> 00:25:33.465 line:95%,end
so you-- it showed on your face.

00:25:33.565 --> 00:25:35.166 line:95%,end
You're not her dance teacher,
so don't give her critiques.

00:25:35.233 --> 00:25:36.234 line:95%,end
I'm not her dance teacher,
but those knees were bent,

00:25:36.301 --> 00:25:37.936 line:95%,end
and she missed many a steps.

00:25:38.003 --> 00:25:39.838 line:95%,end
KELLY: You shouldn't talk about kids.

00:25:39.971 --> 00:25:41.139 line:95%,end
That's rude.

00:25:41.273 --> 00:25:42.741 line:95%,end
[cheering]

00:25:42.807 --> 00:25:44.776 line:95%,end
(SINGING) Living on the dance floor.

00:25:44.843 --> 00:25:46.511 line:95%,end
Before we hear
what all the moms really want to say,

00:25:46.578 --> 00:25:48.446 line:95%,end
let's see a solo performance from Maddie.

