Oh, did you come in the big,
crappy bus from Pittsburgh?

00:34:48.352 --> 00:34:50.688 line:95%,end
- Cathy, go to hell!
- Oh--

00:34:50.755 --> 00:34:52.824 line:95%,end
I feel the earth move under my feet.

00:34:52.957 --> 00:34:54.559 line:95%,end
Ba, ba, ba, boom.
Ba, ba, ba boom.

00:34:54.625 --> 00:34:55.526 line:95%,end
Shut your mouth!

00:34:55.593 --> 00:34:57.261 line:95%,end
- I-- Woo!
- JILL: Shut your mouth!

00:34:57.328 --> 00:35:00.131 line:95%,end
- ABBY: I didn't mean to do that.
- I didn't mean to do that either.

